1. e4 {[%mdl 32768]} e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. O-O Nxe4 5. d4 Nd6 6. Bxc6 dxc6 7. dxe5 Nf5 8. Qxd8+ Kxd8 9. Nc3 a5 10. h3 Ke8 11. Bd2 Ne7 12. Rfe1 Nd5 13. a3 Nxc3 14. Bxc3 Be6 15. Nd4 c5 16. Nxe6 fxe6 17. a4 Be7 18. Rad1 b6 19. Rd3 Rf8 20. g3 Rd8 21. Red1 h5 22. Kg2 g6 23. Rxd8+ Bxd8 24. Rd3 Rf7 25. Bd2 Rd7 26. Rxd7 Kxd7 27. c4 Ke8 28. f4 Kf7 29. Kf3 c6 30. g4 Bh4 {Black retains the h-pawns, trying to prevent the white bishop's penetration on d8, since the white king cannot arrive on g4. It doesn't work anyway.} 31. Ke4 Ke7 (31... hxg4 32. hxg4 Bf2 33. f5 gxf5+ 34. gxf5 Bh4 35. Kf4 Bf2 36. b3 Bh4 37. Kg4 Bd8 38. Bg5 Bc7 39. Kf4 {(Zugzwang.)} exf5 40. Kxf5 Ke8 41. e6 Kf8 42. Bf4 Bd8 43. Bd6+ Ke8 44. Ke4 {(Zugzwang.)} Bh4 45. Bc7 Ke7 46. Kf5 {.}) 32. gxh5 gxh5 33. f5 Kf7 34. b3 Ke7 35. Bh6 Kf7 36. Kf4 Be1 37. Ke4 Bh4 38. Be3 Ke7 39. Bg1 Bg3 40. Be3 Bh4 41. Bc1 Kf7 42. Bh6 $1 Ke7 {Zugwang!} (42... Be1 43. Bg5 {.}) 43. Kf4 Kd7 44. Bf8 Be1 45. Kg5 Bg3 46. Kf6 exf5 47. Kxf5 h4 48. Kf6 Ke8 49. Bd6 Kd7 50. Kf7 Kd8 51. Bb8 Kc8 52. e6 Kxb8 53. e7 Kc7 54. e8=Q 1-0

