{What is Black's next move to both defend and create a threat?} 19... Qd6 $1 {[%mdl 32768] Black is now indirectly defending the vital c3-pawn while simultaneously setting up a threat with another potent move!} ({Also, good enough was} 19... d4 20. O-O e5 {( 20...c2? 21.Rxc8 Qxc8 22.Nxd4= Nd3? 23.Nc6+- )} 21. Rc1 Qd6 {.}) 20. Bf3 (20. Nxc3 Qe5+ 21. Ne2 Qa1+ $1) (20. O-O Ba6 21. Rxa6 Nxa6 22. Qb3 c2 {.}) 20... Ba6 21. Rxf8+ Bxf8 22. Qa5 (22. Qb1 Nd3+ 23. Kf1 Qc5 {, mates!}) 22... Nd3+ 23. Kf1 Ne5 24. Qxc3 (24. Kg2 Nxf3 25. Kxf3 d4 {.}) 24... d4 25. Qb3 Bc4 (25... Bc4 {White decided that he had enough and called it a day due to} 26. Qb7 Nxf3 27. Qxf3 Bd5 {.}) *

