1. Z0 {By the term ‘positive’ we simply refer to a more mobile central majority, than the opponent’s flank one - simple as that! Mobility is rather important, as it can lead to several positive elements, such as passed pawns, restriction of the enemy pieces, the initiative, and other assets.} *

