14... f5 $1 {[%mdl 32768] An excellent idea, aiming to create a mobile pawn majority on the centre/kingside. Black will exchange his c-pawn with White's d-pawn and obtain a 4:3 majority on the centre/kingside, which will be able to advance menacingly. On the contrary, White's 3:2 queenside majority will remain immobile for several moves or, even worse, will never succeed in becoming threatening.} *

