39. f5 $2 {[%mdl 32768] Ping-pong of time-trouble mistakes.} c3 $1 {Decisive - Black wins the white knight!} 40. Nxc3 (40. Qe3 cxb2 41. Qe6+ Kg7 42. fxg6 Rb7) 40... Qf4+ 41. Ke1 (41. Qxf4 Rxb2+ 42. Kg3 Nxf4 43. Kxf4 a5) 41... Qg3+ 42. Kd1 Rxc3 43. Rb8+ (43. fxg6 Qf3+ 44. Qe2 Qh1+ 45. Qe1 Rc1+) 43... Kg7 44. Rb7+ Kf6 45. fxg6 Qf3+ 46. Qe2 Qh1+ {White resigned due to 47.Qe1 Qxd5+ 48.Qd2 Qh1+ 49.Qe1 Rd3+ 50.Kc2 Qxe1 51.Kxd3 Qf1+ 52.Kd4 Qf2+ 53.Kc3 Qf3+ .} *

