[PlyCount "1"]
[EventDate "2024.??.??"]
[SourceTitle "https://www.chessable.co"]

{To exchange or not to exchange the queens?} 17... Qc7 $1 {[%mdl 32768] A simple move, yet at the same time difficult to find. It is not so easy voluntarily to place the queen opposite an enemy rook. But this move is part of a plan to provoke White into opening-up the game on the queenside, which could only favour Black and his mobile majority.} *

