{We need to precise now. How do we proceed without allowing any uncesssarsy counterplay?} 23... g6 $1 {[%mdl 32768]} ({Black carefully avoids any back-rank tricks. Not much is gained by} 23... Rd2 $2 24. Bg4 $1 {( 24.Rc2 Rd8 ( 24...Bd5? 25.Qe8 ) 25.Qb7 Qxb7 26.Bxb7 $15 )} Qd6 25. Bxe6 fxe6 26. Qa8+ Qd8 27. Qxd8+ Rxd8 28. b3 {.}) *

