{The respective pawn structures have radically clarified. Both sides have obtained a 4:3 majority - White on the queenside and Black on the kingside. The two sides' plans must be adapted to comply with the situation. What to do now?} 22... Rf8 $1 {[%cal Gf7f5][%mdl 32768] A logical regrouping of the black pieces, fully in line with the requirements of the position. The black pieces will be transferred to the kingside where, in conjunction with the ...f5 advance, they will seek to grab the initiative and eventually prove that it is more dangerous than White's on the queenside.} *

