{Given White's 4:3 pawn majority on the kingside, what is the best strategy for White to capitalize on this advantage, considering the current board position?} 15. f4 $1 {[%mdl 32768] The pawn structures have defined the field of action for each side. White has a 4:3 majority on the kingside and Black a similar one on the queenside.} *

