{Where do each of White's pieces belong?} 29. Ne5 $1 {[%mdl 32768] Also improving the knight. From its future square on c4, it will exert pressure on the weak black b6-pawn.} Qd5 30. Nc4 {[%csl Rb6,Gc4] The best square for the knight.} Nd7 31. b3 {[%csl Gc4][%cal Gb3c4] Mission completed! The queen is no longer tied to the defence of the c4-knight. Now the next steps for White must be the mobilisation of the king and his kingside majority.} *

