{What move should White make to initiate a strategic advance, setting the stage for a potential minority attack on Black's queenside?} 12. c4 $1 {[%mdl 32768] And now the pawns on the queenside will start marching forward!} *

[Event "The Strategy Instructors Volume 1: Pawn "]
[Site "?"]
[Date "2024.05.28"]
[Round "?"]
[White "5.1) Passive Defense"]
[Black "Moutousis, Konstantinos vs. Gr"]
