1... Ne8 $1 {[%mdl 32768]} 2. Ne2 Nd6 {[%cal Gd6e4,Gd6c4] This is a really superb post for the knight, as it's now very difficult for White to achieve any of his desired pawn levers (b4-b5 or e3-e4). The game now sees steady simplification after which nobody has much to play for.} *

