{A typical minority attack for which Black seems to be fully prepared! So what to do?} 14... b5 $1 {[%cal Gd7b6,Gb6c4][%mdl 32768] A black knight is prepared to enter safely the c4-square sooner or later.} 15. Qc2 axb4 16. axb4 Nd6 $1 {[%cal Gd6c4] Avoiding future exchanges which would ease White's position. The d6-knight is a much more useful piece than any of its opposing knights.} *

[Event "The Strategy Instructors Volume 1: Pawn "]
[Site "?"]
[Date "2024.05.28"]
