15. Qxc3 $6 {[%mdl 32768]} ({White should definitely take out Black's remaining knight via} 15. Bxc7 Qxc7 16. Qxc3 {. White probably missed Black's clever sixteenth move.}) {How to get to our ideal square now?} 15... Bd6 16. Bxd6 Nb5 $1 {[%cal Gb5d6,Gd6c4] Very clever. Now Black's knight gets to the ideal square and it becomes much easier for him to advance on the kingside than it is for White to make progress on the other flank.} *

